{"tid":409764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那禁民眾去日本】日本人：「今年最令人高興的新聞！」","createTime":"2017-09-22T10:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T01:27:22.000Z","uid":29314,"like":114,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9b047ca5284e1151e19b290992c1fe14d2b4b1","tid":409764,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"日本新聞網（Japan News Network）報道，中國當局本月中旬對內地旅行社發出通知，要求限制前往日本的旅行團數目。日本網民普遍對報道反應正面，有人直言是「今年最令人高興的新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n訪日中國遊客數目屢創新高，在日本大小城市都不難見到他們的蹤影。對於中國當局限制訪日遊客數目的報道，有網民表示：「真是非常感激。無論去到哪個觀光勝地，遊客都多得令人幾乎想：『這裡是日本？』記得沖繩的情況尤其嚴重。」<br />\n<br />\n有網民趁機發洩不滿：「今個夏天入住沖繩的酒店，中國人住客從泳池回到酒店房，身也不抹濕漉漉搭電梯，留下處處水漬。心想：不是吧？」有網民早前到訪山梨縣著名的湧泉群「忍野八海」，憶述：「約9成都是中國人，嚇了一跳&hellip;&hellip;去到哪裡都是大聲呼叫，又霸佔店內的桌子。」<br />\n<br />\n不少人都期待中國遊客減少，為當地帶來變化。有人說：「我認為銀座及心齋橋會變得清靜。終於可享受在百貨店好好購物。」也有人說：「去到哪裡都滿是中國人，減少些人數真好&hellip;&hellip;考慮到利益的話，經營商店的人也許會感到不滿，但對一般市民來說，就是不可多得的事。」"},{"pid":"0dd1cd74bca8a8c7dc4ae5511b43c633d925dd87","tid":409764,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"共產黨好嘢,呢鑊我撐你喇"},{"pid":"194876d2e1ab933a855dd2932b965b18b72e00a6","tid":409764,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"包唔包中國香港？"},{"pid":"90a70003fad4acb7bf6384e185fe69637055734e","tid":409764,"uid":14607,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>包唔包中國香港？</blockquote><br />\n香港人冇得去日本暴動都似<br />\nBtw中你老母國香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc6e9c489896679f866e1add9fa2909273b8150","tid":409764,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T21:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37e66f8f7b2384524dc149d4b3ebdf553b1b752","tid":409764,"uid":78304,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T21:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>包唔包中國香港？</blockquote><br />\n包你老母生花柳死"},{"pid":"84d0c3a2876a49f016aa471c0036a2721f8d7968","tid":409764,"uid":7534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T21:36:19.000Z","msg":"勿開心得太早，支那人不是那麼容易對付的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76164bab183435dec31403c2161c7bb79a0c1d87","tid":409764,"uid":37713,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T21:51:02.000Z","msg":"其實心齋橋無左蝗咪就淨返香港台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好出醜比人睇啦下 又唔係唔知有啲香港人成撚隻蝗咁"},{"pid":"6ab2c2410fd85419d2f58f6f61ee6270c73c0335","tid":409764,"uid":67280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T22:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>包唔包中國香港？</blockquote><br />\n香港中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你隻支那狗竟敢分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e666aea172429676acba1363c31472ec96a16ef","tid":409764,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T23:04:07.000Z","msg":"同香港人反應一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90cf8fba96fcfd7fd21c18faff147e72fdcc57e","tid":409764,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T23:06:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人知點解大陸要咁做？"},{"pid":"980694547718b0b73e7883077fd3e48aea3a8afe","tid":409764,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T23:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知點解大陸要咁做？</blockquote><br />\nexport太多"},{"pid":"bc87c9daf9396f6aeca49fc1efe835b52ea19f4f","tid":409764,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實心齋橋無左蝗咪就淨返香港台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好出醜比人睇啦下 又唔係唔知有啲香港人成撚隻蝗咁</blockquote><br />\n好多韓妹架喎"},{"pid":"38bcfae071fa6ebbc77f0b27f12181349fba6adc","tid":409764,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,